Happy New Year greetings.

266
00:13:09,372 --> 00:13:10,915
-By text?
-Yeah.

267
00:13:14,335 --> 00:13:17,505
The mood was so languid in <i>Terrace House.</i>

268
00:13:17,588 --> 00:13:19,549
Because of Natsumi's tone.
Like the way she says,

269
00:13:19,632 --> 00:13:23,386
"Really?"
