294
00:14:34,749 --> 00:14:38,878
-I see.
-So the way she asks

295
00:14:38,961 --> 00:14:41,005
won't make people feel bad.

296
00:14:41,089 --> 00:14:44,967
And in fact, they could get to know
each other and make friends in this way.

297
00:14:45,051 --> 00:14:47,762
From Natsumi's point of view,
that's all it is.

298
00:14:47,845 --> 00:14:49,764
You're right. I see.

299
00:14:49,847 --> 00:14:53,726
But now that there's someone
from Kansai in <i>Terrace House,</i>

300
00:14:53,810 --> 00:14:55,978
we'll get to hear, "Why not?"

301
00:14:56,062 --> 00:14:57,647
"I love you."

302
00:14:57,730 --> 00:15:00,274
